",\n      \"solution\": \"依题可知，$\\\\bar{x} = 2.1, s^2 = 0.01$，所以 $Y \\\\sim N(2.1, 0.1)$，故 $P(Y > 2) = P(Y > 2.1 - 0.1) = P(Y < 2.1 + 0.1) \\\\approx 0.8413 > 0.5$，C正确，D错误；因为 $X \\\\sim N(1.8, 0.1)$，所以 $P(X > 2) = P(X > 1.8 + 2 \\\\times 0.1)$，因为 $P(X < 1.8 + 0.1) \\\\approx 0.8413$，所以 $P(X > 1.8 + 0.1) \\\\approx 1 - 0.8413 = 0.1587 < 0.2$，而 $P(X > 2) = P(X > 1.8 + 2 \\\\times 0.1) < P(X > 1.8 + 0.1) < 0.2$，B正确，A错误，故选：BC.\",\n      \"comment\": \"\",\n      \"knowledge_points\": [\"正态分布\", \"3σ原则\", \"概率计算\"],\n      \"difficulty\": 3,\n      \"bbox\": [85, 212, 907, 478],\n      \"region_json\": {\n        \"x1\": 0,\n        \"y1\": 0,\n        \"x2\": 1000,\n        \"y2\": 2000\n      },\n      \"confidence\": 0.98,\n      \"images\": [],\n      \"page_end\": 6,\n      \"need_review_reason\": \"\",\n      \"raw_explanation\": \"\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"question_no\": \"10\",\n      \"section_title\": \"二、选择题\",\n      \"question_type\": \"unknown\",\n      \"stem\": \"设函数 $f(x) = (x-1)^2(x-4)$，则（ ）\",\n      \"options\": [],\n      \"answer\": \"\",\n      \"analysis\": \"\",\n      \"solution\": \"\",\n      \"comment\": \"\",\n      \"knowledge_points\": [],\n      \"difficulty\": 2,\n      \"bbox\": [87, 855, 447, 880],\n      \"region_json\": {\n        \"x1\": 0,\n        \"y1\": 0,\n        \"x2\": 1000,\n        \"y2\": 2000\n      },\n      \"confidence\": 0.85,\n      \"images\": [],\n      \"page_end\": 6,\n      \"need_review_reason\": \"题目未给出选项，无法判断题型及答案\",\n      \"raw_explanation\": \"\"\n    }\n  ]\n}', 1, NULL, 31172, '2026-05-08 14:50:57.017534', 1, 39, NULL);
INSERT INTO `tiku_ai_parse_result` VALUES (40, 'qwen3-vl-plus', NULL, NULL, '\"{\\\"choices\\\": [{\\\"message\\\": {\\\"content\\\": \\\"{\\\\n  \\\\\\\"page_no\\\\\\\": 7,\\\\n  \\\\\\\"questions\\\\\\\": [\\\\n    {\\\\n      \\\\\\\"question_no\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"10\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"section_title\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"一、选择题\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"question_type\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"single_choice\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"stem\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"A. $x=3$ 是 $f(x)$ 的极小值点\\\\\\\\nB. 当 $0<x<1$ 时，$f(x)<f\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\left(x^{2}\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\right)$\\\\\\\\nC. 当 $1<x<2$ 时，$-4<f(2x-1)<0$\\\\\\\\nD. 当 $-1<x<0$ 时，$f(2-x)>f(x)$\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"options\\\\\\\": [\\\\n        {\\\\n          \\\\\\\"label\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"A\\\\\\\",\\\\n          \\\\\\\"content\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"$x=3$ 是 $f(x)$ 的极小值点\\\\\\\",\\\\n          \\\\\\\"bbox\\\\\\\": [87, 63, 302, 82]\\\\n        },\\\\n        {\\\\n          \\\\\\\"label\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"B\\\\\\\",\\\\n          \\\\\\\"content\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"当 $0<x<1$ 时，$f(x)<f\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\left(x^{2}\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\right)$\\\\\\\",\\\\n          \\\\\\\"bbox\\\\\\\": [498, 55, 765, 80]\\\\n        },\\\\n        {\\\\n          \\\\\\\"label\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"C\\\\\\\",\\\\n          \\\\\\\"content\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"当 $1<x<2$ 时，$-4<f(2x-1)<0$\\\\\\\",\\\\n          \\\\\\\"bbox\\\\\\\": [87, 100, 388, 125]\\\\n        },\\\\n        {\\\\n          \\\\\\\"label\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"D\\\\\\\",\\\\n          \\\\\\\"content\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"当 $-1<x<0$ 时，$f(2-x)>f(x)$\\\\\\\",\\\\n          \\\\\\\"bbox\\\\\\\": [498, 98, 792, 125]\\\\n        }\\\\n      ],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"answer\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"ACD\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"analysis\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"【分析】求出函数 $f(x)$ 的导数，得到极值点，即可判断 A；利用函数的单调性可判断 B；根据函数 $f(x)$ 在 $(1,3)$ 上的值域即可判断 C；直接作差可判断 D.\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"solution\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"【详解】对 A，因为函数 $f(x)$ 的定义域为 $\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\mathbf{R}$，而 $f\'(x)=2(x-1)(x-4)+(x-1)^2=3(x-1)(x-3)$，易知当 $x\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\in(1,3)$ 时，$f\'(x)<0$，当 $x\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\in(-\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\infty,1)$ 或 $x\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\in(3,+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\infty)$ 时，$f\'(x)>0$，函数 $f(x)$ 在 $(-\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\infty,1)$ 上单调递增，在 $(1,3)$ 上单调递减，在 $(3,+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\infty)$ 上单调递增，故 $x=3$ 是函数 $f(x)$ 的极小值点，正确；\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n对 B，当 $0<x<1$ 时，$x-x^2=x(1-x)>0$，所以 $1>x>x^2>0$，而由上可知，函数 $f(x)$ 在 $(0,1)$ 上单调递增，所以 $f(x)>f(x^2)$，错误；\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n对 C，当 $1<x<2$ 时，$1<2x-1<3$，而由上可知，函数 $f(x)$ 在 $(1,3)$ 上单调递减，所以 $f(1)>f(2x-1)>f(3)$，即 $-4<f(2x-1)<0$，正确；\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n对 D，当 $-1<x<0$ 时，$f(2-x)-f(x)=(1-x)^2(-2-x)-(x-1)^2(x-4)=(x-1)^2(2-2x)>0$，所以 $f(2-x)>f(x)$，正确；\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n故选：ACD.\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"comment\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"knowledge_points\\\\\\\": [\\\\\\\"导数与函数单调性\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"极值点判定\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"函数不等式比较\\\\\\\"],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"difficulty\\\\\\\": 3,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"bbox\\\\\\\": [85, 55, 910, 750],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"region_json\\\\\\\": {\\\\n        \\\\\\\"x1\\\\\\\": 0,\\\\n        \\\\\\\"y1\\\\\\\": 0,\\\\n        \\\\\\\"x2\\\\\\\": 1000,\\\\n        \\\\\\\"y2\\\\\\\": 2000\\\\n      },\\\\n      \\\\\\\"confidence\\\\\\\": 0.98,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"images\\\\\\\": [],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"page_end\\\\\\\": 7,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"need_review_reason\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"raw_explanation\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n    },\\\\n    {\\\\n      \\\\\\\"question_no\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"11\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"section_title\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"一、选择题\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"question_type\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"single_choice\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"stem\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"造型 $\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\boldsymbol{y}$ 可以做成美丽的丝带，将其看作图中曲线 $C$ 的一部分．已知 $C$ 过坐标原点 $O$，且 $C$ 上的点满足横坐标大于 $-2$，到点 $F(2,0)$ 的距离与到定直线 $x=a(a<0)$ 的距离之积为 4，则（ ）\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"options\\\\\\\": [],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"answer\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"analysis\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"solution\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"comment\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\