\"label\": \"A\",\n          \"content\": \"$x=3$ 是 $f(x)$ 的极小值点\",\n          \"bbox\": [87, 63, 302, 82]\n        },\n        {\n          \"label\": \"B\",\n          \"content\": \"当 $0<x<1$ 时，$f(x)<f\\\\left(x^{2}\\\\right)$\",\n          \"bbox\": [498, 55, 765, 80]\n        },\n        {\n          \"label\": \"C\",\n          \"content\": \"当 $1<x<2$ 时，$-4<f(2x-1)<0$\",\n          \"bbox\": [87, 100, 388, 125]\n        },\n        {\n          \"label\": \"D\",\n          \"content\": \"当 $-1<x<0$ 时，$f(2-x)>f(x)$\",\n          \"bbox\": [498, 98, 792, 125]\n        }\n      ],\n      \"answer\": \"ACD\",\n      \"analysis\": \"【分析】求出函数 $f(x)$ 的导数，得到极值点，即可判断 A；利用函数的单调性可判断 B；根据函数 $f(x)$ 在 $(1,3)$ 上的值域即可判断 C；直接作差可判断 D.\",\n      \"solution\": \"【详解】对 A，因为函数 $f(x)$ 的定义域为 $\\\\mathbf{R}$，而 $f\'(x)=2(x-1)(x-4)+(x-1)^2=3(x-1)(x-3)$，易知当 $x\\\\in(1,3)$ 时，$f\'(x)<0$，当 $x\\\\in(-\\\\infty,1)$ 或 $x\\\\in(3,+\\\\infty)$ 时，$f\'(x)>0$，函数 $f(x)$ 在 $(-\\\\infty,1)$ 上单调递增，在 $(1,3)$ 上单调递减，在 $(3,+\\\\infty)$ 上单调递增，故 $x=3$ 是函数 $f(x)$ 的极小值点，正确；\\n\\n对 B，当 $0<x<1$ 时，$x-x^2=x(1-x)>0$，所以 $1>x>x^2>0$，而由上可知，函数 $f(x)$ 在 $(0,1)$ 上单调递增，所以 $f(x)>f(x^2)$，错误；\\n\\n对 C，当 $1<x<2$ 时，$1<2x-1<3$，而由上可知，函数 $f(x)$ 在 $(1,3)$ 上单调递减，所以 $f(1)>f(2x-1)>f(3)$，即 $-4<f(2x-1)<0$，正确；\\n\\n对 D，当 $-1<x<0$ 时，$f(2-x)-f(x)=(1-x)^2(-2-x)-(x-1)^2(x-4)=(x-1)^2(2-2x)>0$，所以 $f(2-x)>f(x)$，正确；\\n\\n故选：ACD.\",\n      \"comment\": \"\",\n      \"knowledge_points\": [\"导数与函数单调性\", \"极值点判定\", \"函数不等式比较\"],\n      \"difficulty\": 3,\n      \"bbox\": [85, 55, 910, 750],\n      \"region_json\": {\n        \"x1\": 0,\n        \"y1\": 0,\n        \"x2\": 1000,\n        \"y2\": 2000\n      },\n      \"confidence\": 0.98,\n      \"images\": [],\n      \"page_end\": 7,\n      \"need_review_reason\": \"\",\n      \"raw_explanation\": \"\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"question_no\": \"11\",\n      \"section_title\": \"一、选择题\",\n      \"question_type\": \"single_choice\",\n      \"stem\": \"造型 $\\\\boldsymbol{y}$ 可以做成美丽的丝带，将其看作图中曲线 $C$ 的一部分．已知 $C$ 过坐标原点 $O$，且 $C$ 上的点满足横坐标大于 $-2$，到点 $F(2,0)$ 的距离与到定直线 $x=a(a<0)$ 的距离之积为 4，则（ ）\",\n      \"options\": [],\n      \"answer\": \"\",\n      \"analysis\": \"\",\n      \"solution\": \"\",\n      \"comment\": \"\",\n      \"knowledge_points\": [\"解析几何\", \"轨迹方程\", \"距离公式\"],\n      \"difficulty\": 4,\n      \"bbox\": [87, 770, 908, 838],\n      \"region_json\": {\n        \"x1\": 0,\n        \"y1\": 0,\n        \"x2\": 1000,\n        \"y2\": 2000\n      },\n      \"confidence\": 0.85,\n      \"images\": [\n        {\n          \"bbox\": [165, 772, 185, 788],\n          \"image_type\": \"handwriting\",\n          \"description\": \"手写符号 \'y\'，表示造型符号\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"page_end\": 7,\n      \"need_review_reason\": \"题目提及‘图中曲线C’，但当前页面未显示对应图形，需确认是否跨页或缺失图；选项内容缺失，需人工复核完整题目\",\n      \"raw_explanation\": \"\"\n    }\n  ]\n}', 1, NULL, 36916, '2026-05-08 14:51:33.980391', 1, 40, NULL);
INSERT INTO `tiku_ai_parse_result` VALUES (41, 'qwen3-vl-plus', NULL, NULL, '\"{\\\"choices\\\": [{\\\"message\\\": {\\\"content\\\": \\\"{\\\\n  \\\\\\\"page_no\\\\\\\": 8,\\\\n  \\\\\\\"questions\\\\\\\": [\\\\n    {\\\\n      \\\\\\\"question_no\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"1\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"section_title\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"question_type\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"single_choice\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"stem\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"（题目题干未完整显示，但根据选项与解析可推断为关于曲线C的性质判断题）\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"options\\\\\\\": [\\\\n        {\\\\n          \\\\\\\"label\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"A\\\\\\\",\\\\n          \\\\\\\"content\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"a = -2\\\\\\\",\\\\n          \\\\\\\"bbox\\\\\\\": [87, 215, 164, 235]\\\\n        },\\\\n        {\\\\n          \\\\\\\"label\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"B\\\\\\\",\\\\n          \\\\\\\"content\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"点(2√2, 0)在C上\\\\\\\",\\\\n          \\\\\\\"bbox\\\\\\\": [497, 210, 668, 238]\\\\n        },\\\\n        {\\\\n          \\\\\\\"label\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"C\\\\\\\",\\\\n          \\\\\\\"content\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"C在第一象限的点的纵坐标的最大值为1\\\\\\\",\\\\n          \\\\\\\"bbox\\\\\\\": [87, 275, 423, 295]\\\\n        },\\\\n        {\\\\n          \\\\\\\"label\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"D\\\\\\\",\\\\n          \\\\\\\"content\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"当点(x₀, y₀)在C上时，y₀ ≤ 4/(x₀ + 2)\\\\\\\",\\\\n          \\\\\\\"bbox\\\\\\\": [497, 260, 807, 295]\\\\n        }\\\\n      ],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"answer\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"ABD\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"analysis\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"根据题设将原点代入曲线方程后可求a，故可判断A的正误；结合曲线方程可判断B的正误；利用特例法可判断C的正误；将曲线方程化简后结合不等式的性质可判断D的正误。\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"solution\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"对于A：设曲线上的动点P(x,y)，则x > -2且√[(x−2)² + y²] × |x−a| = 4，因为曲线过坐标原点，故√[(0−2)² + 0²] × |0−a| = 4，解得a = −2，故A正确。对于B：又曲线方程为√[(x−2)² + y²] × |x+2| = 4，而x > −2，故√[(x−2)² + y²] × (x+2) = 4。当x = 2√2, y = 0时，√[(2√2−2)²] × (2√2+2) = (2√2−2)(2√2+2) = 8−4 = 4，故(2√2, 0)在曲线上，故B正确。对于C：由曲线的方程可得y² = 16/(x+2)² − (x−2)²，取x = 3/2，则y² = 64/49 − 1/4 = (256−49)/(49×4) = 207/196 > 1，故此时y² > 1，故C在第一象限内点的纵坐标的最大值大于1，故C错误。\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"comment\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"本题考查含绝对值与根式的曲线方程性质分析，需灵活运用代入法、特例法与代数变形，注意定义域限制x > -2。\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"knowledge_points\\\\\\\": [\\\\\\\"曲线方程与几何性质\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"绝对值与根式运算\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"不等式应用\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"函数最值分析\\\\\\\"],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"difficulty\\\\\\\": 4,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"bbox\\\\\\\": [85, 48, 810, 830],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"region_json\\\\\\\": {\\\\n        \\\\\\\"x1\\\\\\\": 0,\\\\n        \\\\\\\"y1\\\\\\\": 0,\\\\n        \\\\\\\"x2\\\\\\\": 1000,\\\\n        \\\\\\\"y2\\\\\\\": 2000\\\\n      },\\\\n      \\\\\\\"confidence\\\\\\\": 0.98,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"images\\\\\\\": [\\\\n        {\\\\n          \\\\\\\"bbox\\\\\\\": [100, 50, 298, 200],\\\\n          \\\\\\\"image_type\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"diagram\\\\\\\",\\\\n          \\\\\\\"description\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"平面直角坐标系中的一条曲线C，包含过原点O的左支（类似抛物线开口向左下）和右支（椭圆或闭合曲线的一部分），x轴上标有焦点F\\\\\\\"\\\\n        }\\\\n      ],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"page_end\\\\\\\": 8,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"need_review_reason\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"raw_explanation\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"【答案】ABD\\\\\\\\n【解析】\\\\\\\\n【分析】根据题设将原点代入曲线方程后可求a，故可判断A的正误，结合曲线方程可判断B的正误，利用特例法可判断C的正误，将曲线方程化简后结合不等式的性质可判断D的正误.\\\\\\\\n【详解】对于A：设曲线上的动点P(x,y)，则x > -2且√[(x−2)² + y²] × |x−a| = 4，因为曲线过坐标原点，故√[(0−2)² + 0²] × |0−a| = 4，解得a = −2，故A正确.\\\\\\\\n对于B：又曲线方程为√[(x−2)² + y²] × |x+2| = 4，而x > −2，故√[(x−2)² + y²] × (x+2) = 4.\\\\\\\\n当x = 2√2, y = 0时，√[(2√2−2)²] × (2√2+2) = 8−4 = 4，故(2√2, 0)在曲线上，故B正确.\\\\\\\\n对于C：由曲线的方程可得y² = 16/(x+2)² − (x−2)²，取x = 3/2，则y² = 64/49 − 1/4 = 64/49 − 49/196 = (256−49)/196 = 207/196 > 1，故此时y² > 1，故C在第一象限内点的纵坐标的最大值大于1，故C错误.\\\\\\\"\\\\n    }\\\\n  ]\\\\n}\\\", \\\"reasoning_content\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"role\\\": \\\"assistant\\\"}, \\\"finish_reason\\\": \\\"stop\\\", \\\"index\\\": 0, \\\"logprobs\\\": null}], \\\"object\\\": \\\"chat.completion\\\", \\\"usage\\\": {\\\"prompt_tokens\\\": 3583, \\\"completion_tokens\\\": 1383, \\\"total_tokens\\\": 4966, \\\"completion_tokens_details\\\": {\\\"text_tokens\\\": 1383}, \\\"prompt_tokens_details\\\": {\\\"image_tokens\\\": 2522, \\\"text_tokens\\\": 1061, \\\"cached_tokens\\\": 0}}, \\\"created\\\": 1778251939, \\\"system_fingerprint\\\": null, \\\"model\\\": \\\"qwen3-vl-plus\\\", \\\"id\\\": \\\"chatcmpl-8aa73716-13d5-9550-9f39-639b6750cd64\\\"}\"', '{\n  \"page_no\": 8,\n  \"questions\": [\n    {\n      \"question_no\": \"1\",\n      \"section_title\": \"\",\n      \"question_type\": \"single_choice\",\n      \"stem\": \"（题目题干未完整显示，但根据选项与解析可推断为关于曲线C的性质判断题）\",\n      \"options\": [\n        {\n          \"label\": \"A\",\n          \"content\": \"a = -2\",\n          \"bbox\": [87, 215, 164, 235]\n        },\n        {\n          \"label\": \"B\",\n          \"content\": \"点(2√2, 0)在C上\",\n          \"bbox\": [497, 210, 668, 238]\n        },\n        {\n          \"label\": \"C\",\n          \"content\": \"C在第一象限的点的纵坐标的最大值为1\",\n          \"bbox\": [87, 275, 423, 295]\n        },\n        {\n          \"label\": \"D\",\n          \"content\": \"当点(x₀, y₀)在C上时，y₀ ≤ 4/(x₀ + 2)\",\n          \"bbox\": [497, 260, 807, 295]\n        }\n      ],\n      \"answer\": \"ABD\",\n      \"analysis\": \"根据题设将原点代入曲线方程后可求a，故可判断A的正误；结合曲线方程可判断B的正误；利用特例法可判断C的正误；将曲线方程化简后结合不等式的性质可判断D的正误。\",\n      \"solution\": \"对于A：设曲线上的动点P(x,y)，则x > -2且√[(x−2)² + y²] × |x−a| = 4，因为曲线过坐标原点，故√[(0−2)² + 0²] × |0−a| = 4，解得a = −2，故A正确。对于B：又曲线方程为√[(x−2)² + y²] × |x+2| = 4，而x > −2，故√[(x−2)² + y²] × (x+2) = 4。当x = 2√2, y = 0时，√[(2√2−2)²] × (2√2+2) = (2√2−2)(2√2+2) = 8−4 = 4，故(2√2, 0)在曲线上，故B正确。对于C：由曲线的方程可得y² = 16/(x+2)² − (x−2)²，取x = 3/2，则y² = 64/49 − 1/4 = (256−49)/(49×4) = 207/196 > 1，故此时y² > 1，故C在第一象限内点的纵坐标的最大值大于1，故C错误。\",\n      \"comment\": \"本题考查含绝对值与根式的曲线方程性质分析，需灵活运用代入法、特例法与代数变形，注意定义域限制x > -2。\",\n      \"knowledge_points\": [\"曲线方程与几何性质\", \"绝对值与根式运算\", \"不等式应用\", \"函数最值分析\"],\n      \"difficulty\": 4,\n      \"bbox\": [85, 48, 810, 830],\n      \"region_json\": {\n        \"x1\": 0,\n        \"y1\": 0,\n        \"x2\": 1000,\n        \"y2\": 2000\n      },\n      \"confidence\": 0.98,\n      \"images\": [\n        {\n          \"bbox\": [100, 50, 298, 200],\n          \"image_type\": \"diagram\",\n          \"description\": \"平面直角坐标系中的一条曲线C，包含过原点O的左支（类似抛物线开口向左下）和右支（椭圆或闭合曲线的一部分），x轴上标有焦点F\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"page_end\": 8,\n      \"need_review_reason\": \"\",\n      \"raw_explanation\": \"【答案】ABD\\n【解析】\\n【分析】根据题设将原点代入曲线方程后可求a，故可判断A的正误，结合曲线方程可判断B的正误，利用特例法可判断C的正误，将曲线方程化简后结合不等式的性质可判断D的正误.\\n【详解】对于A：设曲线上的动点P(x,y)，则x > -2且√[(x−2)² + y²] × |x−a| = 4，因为曲线过坐标原点，故√[(0−2)² + 0²] × |0−a| = 4，解得a = −2，故A正确.\\n对于B：又曲线方程为√[(x−2)² + y²] × |x+2| = 4，而x > −2，故√[(x−2)² + y²] × (x+2) = 4.\\n当x = 2√2, y = 0时，√[(2√2−2)²] × (2√2+2) = 8−4 = 4，故(2√2, 0)在曲线上，故B正确.\\n对于C：由曲线的方程可得y² = 16/(x+2)² − (x−2)²，取x = 3/2，则y² = 64/49 − 1/4 = 64/49 − 49/196 = (256−49)/196 = 207/196 > 1，故此时y² > 1，故C在第一象限内点的纵坐标的最大值大于1，故C错误.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}', 1, NULL, 44485, '2026-05-08 14:52:18.513154', 1, 41, NULL);
INSERT INTO `tiku_ai_parse_result` VALUES (42, 'qwen3-vl-plus', NULL, NULL, '\"{\\\"choices\\\": [{\\\"message\\\": {\\\"content\\\": \\\"{\\\\n  \\\\\\\"page_no\\\\\\\": 9,\\\\n  \\\\\\\"questions\\\\\\\": [\\\\n    {\\\\n      \\\\\\\"question_no\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"12\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"section_title\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"三、填空题\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"question_type\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"fill_blank\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"stem\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"设双曲线 $C: \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{x^2}{a^2} - \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{y^2}{b^2} = 1 (a > 0, b > 0)$ 的左右焦点分别为 $F_1$, $F_2$，过 $F_2$ 作平行于 $y$ 轴的直线交 $C$ 于 $A$, $B$ 两点，若 $|F_1A| = 13$, $|AB| = 10$，则 $C$ 的离心率为__________.\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"options\\\\\\\": [],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"answer\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{3}{2}\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"analysis\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"【分析】由题意画出双曲线大致图象，求出 $|AF_2|$，结合双曲线第一定义求出 $|AF_1|$，即可得到 $a,b,c$ 的值，从而求出离心率。\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"solution\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"【详解】由题可知 $A,B,F_2$ 三点横坐标相等，设 $A$ 在第一象限，将 $x = c$ 代入 $\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{x^2}{a^2} - \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{y^2}{b^2} = 1$ 得 $y = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\pm \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{b^2}{a}$，即 $A\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\left(c, \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{b^2}{a}\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\right), B\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\left(c, -\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{b^2}{a}\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\right)$，故 $|AB| = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{2b^2}{a} = 10$，$|AF_2| = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{b^2}{a} = 5$，又 $|AF_1| - |AF_2| = 2a$，得 $|AF_1| = |AF_2| + 2a = 2a + 5 = 13$，解得 $a = 4$，代入 $\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{b^2}{a} = 5$ 得 $b^2 = 20$，故 $c^2 = a^2 + b^2 = 36$，即 $c = 6$，所以 $e = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{c}{a} = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{6}{4} = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{3}{2}$。\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"comment\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"knowledge_points\\\\\\\": [\\\\\\\"双曲线的定义\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"双曲线的标准方程\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"离心率计算\\\\\\\"],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"difficulty\\\\\\\": 4,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"bbox\\\\\\\": [87, 318, 909, 420],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"region_json\\\\\\\": {\\\\\\\"x1\\\\\\\": 87, \\\\\\\"y1\\\\\\\": 318, \\\\\\\"x2\\\\\\\": 909, \\\\\\\"y2\\\\\\\": 420},\\\\n      \\\\\\\"confidence\\\\\\\": 0.98,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"images\\\\\\\": [],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"page_end\\\\\\\": 9,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"need_review_reason\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"raw_explanation\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n    }\\\\n  ]\\\\n}\\\", \\\"reasoning_content\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"role\\\": \\\"assistant\\\"}, \\\"finish_reason\\\": \\\"stop\\\", \\\"index\\\": 0, \\\"logprobs\\\": null}], \\\"object\\\": \\\"chat.completion\\\", \\\"usage\\\": {\\\"prompt_tokens\\\": 3583, \\\"completion_tokens\\\": 699, \\\"total_tokens\\\": 4282, \\\"completion_tokens_details\\\": {\\\"text_tokens\\\": 699}, \\\"prompt_tokens_details\\\": {\\\"image_tokens\\\": 2522, \\\"text_tokens\\\": 1061, \\\"cached_tokens\\\": 0}}, \\\"created\\\": 1778251965, \\\"system_fingerprint\\\": null, \\\"model\\\": \\\"qwen3-vl-plus\\\", \\\"id\\\": \\\"chatcmpl-3b6d4922-7c09-94d6-ba38-41b336e696e8\\\"}\"', '{\n  \"page_no\": 9,\n  \"questions\": [\n    {\n      \"question_no\": \"12\",\n      \"section_title\": \"三、填空题\",\n      \"question_type\": \"fill_blank\",\n      \"stem\": \"设双曲线 $C: \\\\frac{x^2}{a^2} - \\\\frac{y^2}{b^2} = 1 (a > 0, b > 0)$ 的左右焦点分别为 $F_1$, $F_2$，过 $F_2$ 作平行于 $y$ 轴的直线交 $C$ 于 $A$, $B$ 两点，若 $|F_1A| = 13$, $|AB| = 10$，则 $C$ 的离心率为__________.\",\n      \"options\": [],\n      \"answer\": \"\\\\frac{3}{2}\",\n      \"analysis\": \"【分析】由题意画出双曲线大致图象，求出 $|AF_2|$，结合双曲线第一定义求出 $|AF_1|$，即可得到 $a,b,c$ 的值，从而求出离心率。\",\n      \"solution\": \"【详解】由题可知 $A,B,F_2$ 三点横坐标相等，设 $A$ 在第一象限，将 $x = c$ 代入 $\\\\frac{x^2}{a^2} - \\\\frac{y^2}{b^2} = 1$ 得 $y = \\\\pm \\\\frac{b^2}{a}$，即 $A\\\\left(c, \\\\frac{b^2}{a}\\\\right), B\\\\left(c, -\\\\frac{b^2}{a}\\\\right)$，故 $|AB| = \\\\frac{2b^2}{a} = 10$，$|AF_2| = \\\\frac{b^2}{a} = 5$，又 $|AF_1| - |AF_2| = 2a$，得 $|AF_1| = |AF_2| + 2a = 2a + 5 = 13$，解得 $a = 4$，代入 $\\\\frac{b^2}{a} = 5$ 得 $b^2 = 20$，故 $c^2 = a^2 + b^2 = 36$，即 $c = 6$，所以 $e = \\\\frac{c}{a} = \\\\frac{6}{4} = \\\\frac{3}{2}$。\",\n      \"comment\": \"\",\n      \"knowledge_points\": [\"双曲线的定义\", \"双曲线的标准方程\", \"离心率计算\"],\n      \"difficulty\": 4,\n      \"bbox\": [87, 318, 909, 420],\n      \"region_json\": {\"x1\": 87, \"y1\": 318, \"x2\": 909, \"y2\": 420},\n      \"confidence\": 0.98,\n      \"images\": [],\n      \"page_end\": 9,\n      \"need_review_reason\": \"\",\n      \"raw_explanation\": \"\"\n    }\n  ]\n}', 1, NULL, 26547, '2026-05-08 14:52:45.096027', 1, 42, NULL);
INSERT INTO `tiku_ai_parse_result` VALUES (43, 'qwen3-vl-plus', NULL, NULL, '\"{\\\"choices\\\": [{\\\"message\\\": {\\\"content\\\": \\\"{\\\\n  \\\\\\\"page_no\\\\\\\": 10,\\\\n  \\\\\\\"questions\\\\\\\": [\\\\n    {\\\\n      \\\\\\\"question_no\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"13\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"section_title\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"question_type\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"fill_blank\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"stem\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"若曲线 $ y = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\mathrm{e}^x + x $ 在点 $ (0,1) $ 处的切线也是曲线 $ y = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ln(x+1) + a $ 的切线，则 $ a = $ ________.\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"options\\\\\\\": [],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"answer\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"ln 2\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"analysis\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"先求出曲线 $ y = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\mathrm{e}^x + x $ 在 $ (0,1) $ 的切线方程，再设曲线 $ y = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ln(x+1) + a $ 的切点为 $ \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\left(x_0, \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ln(x_0 + 1) + a\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\right) $，求出 $ y\' $，利用公切线斜率相等求出 $ x_0 $，表示出切线方程，结合两切线方程相同即可求解。\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"solution\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"由 $ y = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\mathrm{e}^x + x $ 得 $ y\' = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\mathrm{e}^x + 1 $，$ y\'|_{x=0} = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\mathrm{e}^0 + 1 = 2 $，故曲线 $ y = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\mathrm{e}^x + x $ 在 $ (0,1) $ 处的切线方程为 $ y = 2x + 1 $；\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n由 $ y = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ln(x+1) + a $ 得 $ y\' = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{1}{x+1} $，\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n设切线与曲线 $ y = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ln(x+1) + a $ 相切的切点为 $ \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\left(x_0, \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ln(x_0 + 1) + a\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\right) $，\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n由两曲线有公切线得 $ y\' = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{1}{x_0 + 1} = 2 $，解得 $ x_0 = -\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{1}{2} $，则切点为 $ \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\left(-\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{1}{2}, a + \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ln\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{1}{2}\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\right) $，\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n切线方程为 $ y = 2\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\left(x + \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{1}{2}\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\right) + a + \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ln\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{1}{2} = 2x + 1 + a - \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ln 2 $，\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n根据两切线重合，所以 $ a - \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ln 2 = 0 $，解得 $ a = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ln 2 $。\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"comment\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"knowledge_points\\\\\\\": [\\\\\\\"导数的几何意义\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"公切线问题\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"函数求导\\\\\\\"],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"difficulty\\\\\\\": 4,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"bbox\\\\\\\": [89, 275, 826, 302],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"region_json\\\\\\\": {\\\\n        \\\\\\\"x1\\\\\\\": 0,\\\\n        \\\\\\\"y1\\\\\\\": 0,\\\\n        \\\\\\\"x2\\\\\\\": 1000,\\\\n        \\\\\\\"y2\\\\\\\": 2000\\\\n      },\\\\n      \\\\\\\"confidence\\\\\\\": 0.98,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"images\\\\\\\": [\\\\n        {\\\\n          \\\\\\\"bbox\\\\\\\": [103, 116, 298, 263],\\\\n          \\\\\\\"image_type\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"diagram\\\\\\\",\\\\n          \\\\\\\"description\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"双曲线与直线相交示意图，含焦点F1、F2，原点O，点A、B\\\\\\\"\\\\n        }\\\\n      ],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"page_end\\\\\\\": 10,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"need_review_reason\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"raw_explanation\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"故答案为：ln 2\\\\\\\"\\\\n    }\\\\n  ]\\\\n}\\\", \\\"reasoning_content\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"role\\\": \\\"assistant\\\"}, \\\"finish_reason\\\": \\\"stop\\\", \\\"index\\\": 0, \\\"logprobs\\\": null}], \\\"object\\\": \\\"chat.completion\\\", \\\"usage\\\": {\\\"prompt_tokens\\\": 3583, \\\"completion_tokens\\\": 812, \\\"total_tokens\\\": 4395, \\\"completion_tokens_details\\\": {\\\"text_tokens\\\": 812}, \\\"prompt_tokens_details\\\": {\\\"image_tokens\\\": 2522, \\\"text_tokens\\\": 1061, \\\"cached_tokens\\\": 0}}, \\\"created\\\": 1778251992, \\\"system_fingerprint\\\": null, \\\"model\\\": \\\"qwen3-vl-plus\\\", \\\"id\\\": \\\"chatcmpl-69ac9437-edec-93a9-8b07-71a4c19d02f0\\\"}\"', '{\n  \"page_no\": 10,\n  \"questions\": [\n    {\n      \"question_no\": \"13\",\n      \"section_title\": \"\",\n      \"question_type\": \"fill_blank\",\n      \"stem\": \"若曲线 $ y = \\\\mathrm{e}^x + x $ 在点 $ (0,1) $ 处的切线也是曲线 $ y = \\\\ln(x+1) + a $ 的切线，则 $ a = $ ________.\",\n      \"options\": [],\n      \"answer\": \"ln 2\",\n      \"analysis\": \"先求出曲线 $ y = \\\\mathrm{e}^x + x $ 在 $ (0,1) $ 的切线方程，再设曲线 $ y = \\\\ln(x+1) + a $ 的切点为 $ \\\\left(x_0, \\\\ln(x_0 + 1) + a\\\\right) $，求出 $ y\' $，利用公切线斜率相等求出 $ x_0 $，表示出切线方程，结合两切线方程相同即可求解。\",\n      \"solution\": \"由 $ y = \\\\mathrm{e}^x + x $ 得 $ y\' = \\\\mathrm{e}^x + 1 $，$ y\'|_{x=0} = \\\\mathrm{e}^0 + 1 = 2 $，故曲线 $ y = \\\\mathrm{e}^x + x $ 在 $ (0,1) $ 处的切线方程为 $ y = 2x + 1 $；\\n\\n由 $ y = \\\\ln(x+1) + a $ 得 $ y\' = \\\\frac{1}{x+1} $，\\n\\n设切线与曲线 $ y = \\\\ln(x+1) + a $ 相切的切点为 $ \\\\left(x_0, \\\\ln(x_0 + 1) + a\\\\right) $，\\n\\n由两曲线有公切线得 $ y\' = \\\\frac{1}{x_0 + 1} = 2 $，解得 $ x_0 = -\\\\frac{1}{2} $，则切点为 $ \\\\left(-\\\\frac{1}{2}, a + \\\\ln\\\\frac{1}{2}\\\\right) $，\\n\\n切线方程为 $ y = 2\\\\left(x + \\\\frac{1}{2}\\\\right) + a + \\\\ln\\\\frac{1}{2} = 2x + 1 + a - \\\\ln 2 $，\\n\\n根据两切线重合，所以 $ a - \\\\ln 2 = 0 $，解得 $ a = \\\\ln 2 $。\",\n      \"comment\": \"\",\n      \"knowledge_points\": [\"导数的几何意义\", \"公切线问题\", \"函数求导\"],\n      \"difficulty\": 4,\n      \"bbox\": [89, 275, 826, 302],\n      \"region_json\": {\n        \"x1\": 0,\n        \"y1\": 0,\n        \"x2\": 1000,\n        \"y2\": 2000\n      },\n      \"confidence\": 0.98,\n      \"images\": [\n        {\n          \"bbox\": [103, 116, 298, 263],\n          \"image_type\": \"diagram\",\n          \"description\": \"双曲线与直线相交示意图，含焦点F1、F2，原点O，点A、B\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"page_end\": 10,\n      \"need_review_reason\": \"\",\n      \"raw_explanation\": \"故答案为：ln 2\"\n    }\n  ]\n}', 1, NULL, 28998, '2026-05-08 14:53:14.130200', 1, 43, NULL);
INSERT INTO `tiku_ai_parse_result` VALUES (44, 'qwen3-vl-plus', NULL, NULL, '\"{\\\"choices\\\": [{\\\"message\\\": {\\\"content\\\": \\\"{\\\\n  \\\\\\\"page_no\\\\\\\": 11,\\\\n  \\\\\\\"questions\\\\\\\": [\\\\n    {\\\\n      \\\\\\\"question_no\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"14\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"section_title\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"question_type\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"computation\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"stem\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"甲、乙两人各有四张卡片，每张卡片上标有一个数字，甲的卡片上分别标有数字1，3，5，7，乙的卡片上分别标有数字2，4，6，8，两人进行四轮比赛，在每轮比赛中，两人各自从自己持有的卡片中随机选一张，并比较所选卡片上数字的大小，数字大的人得1分，数字小的人得0分，然后各自弃置此轮所选的卡片（弃置的卡片在此后的轮次中不能使用）.则四轮比赛后，甲的总得分不小于2的概率为________.\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"options\\\\\\\": [],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"answer\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"1/2\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"analysis\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"将每局的得分分别作为随机变量，然后分析其和随机变量即可.\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"solution\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"设甲在四轮游戏中的得分分别为$X_1,X_2,X_3,X_4$，四轮的总得分为$X$。对于任意一轮，甲乙两人在该轮出示每张牌的概率都均等，其中使得甲获胜的出牌组合有六种，从而甲在该轮获胜的概率$P(X_k=1)=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{6}{4\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\times4}=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{3}{8}$，所以$E(X_k)=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{3}{8}(k=1,2,3,4)$。从而$E(X)=E(X_1+X_2+X_3+X_4)=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sum_{k=1}^4 E(X_k)=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sum_{k=1}^4 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{3}{8}=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{3}{2}$。记$p_k=P(X=k)(k=0,1,2,3)$。如果甲得0分，则组合方式是唯一的：必定是甲出1，3，5，7分别对应乙出2，4，6，8，所以$p_0=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{1}{A_4^4}=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{1}{24}$；如果甲得3分，则组合方式也是唯一的：必定是甲出1，3，5，7分别对应乙出8，2，4，6，所以$p_3=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{1}{A_4^4}=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{1}{24}$。而$X$的所有可能取值是0，1，2，3，故$p_0+p_1+p_2+p_3=1$，$p_1+2p_2+3p_3=E(X)=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{3}{2}$。所以$p_1+p_2+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{1}{12}=1$，$p_1+2p_2+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{1}{8}=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{3}{2}$，两式相减即得$p_2+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{1}{24}=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{1}{2}$，故$p_2+p_3=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{1}{2}$。\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"comment\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"knowledge_points\\\\\\\": [\\\\\\\"概率\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"期望\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"排列组合\\\\\\\"],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"difficulty\\\\\\\": 4,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"bbox\\\\\\\": [89, 55, 907, 157],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"region_json\\\\\\\": {\\\\\\\"x1\\\\\\\": 89, \\\\\\\"y1\\\\\\\": 55, \\\\\\\"x2\\\\\\\": 907, \\\\\\\"y2\\\\\\\": 157},\\\\n      \\\\\\\"confidence\\\\\\\": 0.98,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"images\\\\\\\": [],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"page_end\\\\\\\": 11,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"need_review_reason\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"raw_explanation\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"【答案】1/2\\\\\\\\n【解析】\\\\\\\\n【分析】将每局的得分分别作为随机变量，然后分析其和随机变量即可.\\\\\\\\n【详解】设甲在四轮游戏中的得分分别为$X_1,X_2,X_3,X_4$，四轮的总得分为$X$.\\\\\\\\n对于任意一轮，甲乙两人在该轮出示每张牌的概率都均等，其中使得甲获胜的出牌组合有六种，从而甲在该轮获胜的概率$P(X_k=1)=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{6}{4\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\times4}=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{3}{8}$，所以$E(X_k)=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{3}{8}(k=1,2,3,4)$.\\\\\\\\n从而$E(X)=E(X_1+X_2+X_3+X_4)=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sum_{k=1}^4 E(X_k)=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sum_{k=1}^4 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{3}{8}=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{3}{2}$.\\\\\\\\n记$p_k=P(X=k)(k=0,1,2,3)$.\\\\\\\\n如果甲得0分，则组合方式是唯一的：必定是甲出1，3，5，7分别对应乙出2，4，6，8，所以$p_0=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{1}{A_4^4}=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{1}{24}$；\\\\\\\\n如果甲得3分，则组合方式也是唯一的：必定是甲出1，3，5，7分别对应乙出8，2，4，6，所以$p_3=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{1}{A_4^4}=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{1}{24}$.\\\\\\\\n而$X$的所有可能取值是0，1，2，3，故$p_0+p_1+p_2+p_3=1$，$p_1+2p_2+3p_3=E(X)=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{3}{2}$.\\\\\\\\n所以$p_1+p_2+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{1}{12}=1$，$p_1+2p_2+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{1}{8}=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{3}{2}$，两式相减即得$p_2+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{1}{24}=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{1}{2}$，故$p_2+p_3=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{1}{2}$.\\\\\\\"\\\\n    }\\\\n  ]\\\\n}\\\", \\\"reasoning_content\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"role\\\": \\\"assistant\\\"}, \\\"finish_reason\\\": \\\"stop\\\", \\\"index\\\": 0, \\\"logprobs\\\": null}], \\\"object\\\": \\\"chat.completion\\\", \\\"usage\\\": {\\\"prompt_tokens\\\": 3583, \\\"completion_tokens\\\": 1321, \\\"total_tokens\\\": 4904, \\\"completion_tokens_details\\\": {\\\"text_tokens\\\": 1321}, \\\"prompt_tokens_details\\\": {\\\"image_tokens\\\": 2522, \\\"text_tokens\\\": 1061, \\\"cached_tokens\\\": 0}}, \\\"created\\\": 1778252037, \\\"system_fingerprint\\\": null, \\\"model\\\": \\\"qwen3-vl-plus\\\", \\\"id\\\": \\\"chatcmpl-5144322c-e202-9a68-a165-23f401c6c995\\\"}\"', '{\n  \"page_no\": 11,\n  \"questions\": [\n    {\n      \"question_no\": \"14\",\n      \"section_title\": \"\",\n      \"question_type\": \"computation\",\n      \"stem\": \"甲、乙两人各有四张卡片，每张卡片上标有一个数字，甲的卡片上分别标有数字1，3，5，7，乙的卡片上分别标有数字2，4，6，8，两人进行四轮比赛，在每轮比赛中，两人各自从自己持有的卡片中随机选一张，并比较所选卡片上数字的大小，数字大的人得1分，数字小的人得0分，然后各自弃置此轮所选的卡片（弃置的卡片在此后的轮次中不能使用）.则四轮比赛后，甲的总得分不小于2的概率为________.\",\n      \"options\": [],\n      \"answer\": \"1/2\",\n      \"analysis\": \"将每局的得分分别作为随机变量，然后分析其和随机变量即可.\",\n      \"solution\": \"设甲在四轮游戏中的得分分别为$X_1,X_2,X_3,X_4$，四轮的总得分为$X$。对于任意一轮，甲乙两人在该轮出示每张牌的概率都均等，其中使得甲获胜的出牌组合有六种，从而甲在该轮获胜的概率$P(X_k=1)=\\\\frac{6}{4\\\\times4}=\\\\frac{3}{8}$，所以$E(X_k)=\\\\frac{3}{8}(k=1,2,3,4)$。从而$E(X)=E(X_1+X_2+X_3+X_4)=\\\\sum_{k=1}^4 E(X_k)=\\\\sum_{k=1}^4 \\\\frac{3}{8}=\\\\frac{3}{2}$。记$p_k=P(X=k)(k=0,1,2,3)$。如果甲得0分，则组合方式是唯一的：必定是甲出1，3，5，7分别对应乙出2，4，6，8，所以$p_0=\\\\frac{1}{A_4^4}=\\\\frac{1}{24}$；如果甲得3分，则组合方式也是唯一的：必定是甲出1，3，5，7分别对应乙出8，2，4，6，所以$p_3=\\\\frac{1}{A_4^4}=\\\\frac{1}{24}$。而$X$的所有可能取值是0，1，2，3，故$p_0+p_1+p_2+p_3=1$，$p_1+2p_2+3p_3=E(X)=\\\\frac{3}{2}$。所以$p_1+p_2+\\\\frac{1}{12}=1$，$p_1+2p_2+\\\\frac{1}{8}=\\\\frac{3}{2}$，两式相减即得$p_2+\\\\frac{1}{24}=\\\\frac{1}{2}$，故$p_2+p_3=\\\\frac{1}{2}$。\",\n      \"comment\": \"\",\n      \"knowledge_points\": [\"概率\", \"期望\", \"排列组合\"],\n      \"difficulty\": 4,\n      \"bbox\": [89, 55, 907, 157],\n      \"region_json\": {\"x1\": 89, \"y1\": 55, \"x2\": 907, \"y2\": 157},\n      \"confidence\": 0.98,\n      \"images\": [],\n      \"page_end\": 11,\n      \"need_review_reason\": \"\",\n      \"raw_explanation\": \"【答案】1/2\\n【解析】\\n【分析】将每局的得分分别作为随机变量，然后分析其和随机变量即可.\\n【详解】设甲在四轮游戏中的得分分别为$X_1,X_2,X_3,X_4$，四轮的总得分为$X$.\\n对于任意一轮，甲乙两人在该轮出示每张牌的概率都均等，其中使得甲获胜的出牌组合有六种，从而甲在该轮获胜的概率$P(X_k=1)=\\\\frac{6}{4\\\\times4}=\\\\frac{3}{8}$，所以$E(X_k)=\\\\frac{3}{8}(k=1,2,3,4)$.\\n从而$E(X)=E(X_1+X_2+X_3+X_4)=\\\\sum_{k=1}^4 E(X_k)=\\\\sum_{k=1}^4 \\\\frac{3}{8}=\\\\frac{3}{2}$.\\n记$p_k=P(X=k)(k=0,1,2,3)$.\\n如果甲得0分，则组合方式是唯一的：必定是甲出1，3，5，7分别对应乙出2，4，6，8，所以$p_0=\\\\frac{1}{A_4^4}=\\\\frac{1}{24}$；\\n如果甲得3分，则组合方式也是唯一的：必定是甲出1，3，5，7分别对应乙出8，2，4，6，所以$p_3=\\\\frac{1}{A_4^4}=\\\\frac{1}{24}$.\\n而$X$的所有可能取值是0，1，2，3，故$p_0+p_1+p_2+p_3=1$，$p_1+2p_2+3p_3=E(X)=\\\\frac{3}{2}$.\\n所以$p_1+p_2+\\\\frac{1}{12}=1$，$p_1+2p_2+\\\\frac{1}{8}=\\\\frac{3}{2}$，两式相减即得$p_2+\\\\frac{1}{24}=\\\\frac{1}{2}$，故$p_2+p_3=\\\\frac{1}{2}$.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}', 1, NULL, 42690, '2026-05-08 14:53:56.860425', 1, 44, NULL);
INSERT INTO `tiku_ai_parse_result` VALUES (45, 'qwen3-vl-plus', NULL, NULL, '\"{\\\"choices\\\": [{\\\"message\\\": {\\\"content\\\": \\\"{\\\\n  \\\\\\\"page_no\\\\\\\": 12,\\\\n  \\\\\\\"questions\\\\\\\": [\\\\n    {\\\\n      \\\\\\\"question_no\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"15\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"section_title\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"四、解答题\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"question_type\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"computation\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"stem\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"记△ABC内角A、B、C的对边分别为a，b，c，已知$\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sin C = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{2} \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\cos B$，$a^2 + b^2 - c^2 = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{2}ab$。（1）求B；（2）若△ABC的面积为$3+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{3}$，求c。\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"options\\\\\\\": [],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"answer\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"(1) $B = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\pi}{3}$\\\\\\\\n(2) $2\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{2}$\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"analysis\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"【点睛】关键点点睛：本题的关键在于将问题转化为随机变量问题，利用期望的可加性得到等量关系，从而避免繁琐的列举。\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"solution\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"【解析】\\\\\\\\n【分析】（1）由余弦定理、平方关系依次求出$\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\cos C, \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sin C$，最后结合已知$\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sin C = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{2} \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\cos B$得$\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\cos B$的值即可；\\\\\\\\n（2）首先求出$A,B,C$，然后由正弦定理可将$a,b$均用含有$c$的式子表示，结合三角形面积公式即可列方程求解。\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n【小问1详解】\\\\\\\\n由余弦定理有$a^2 + b^2 - c^2 = 2ab\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\cos C$，对比已知$a^2 + b^2 - c^2 = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{2}ab$，\\\\\\\\n可得$\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\cos C = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{a^2 + b^2 - c^2}{2ab} = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{2}ab}{2ab} = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{2}}{2}$，\\\\\\\\n因为$C \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\in (0,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\pi)$，所以$\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sin C > 0$，\\\\\\\\n故$\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sin C = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{1 - \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\cos^2 C} = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{1 - \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\left(\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{2}}{2}\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\right)^2} = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{2}}{2}$，\\\\\\\\n又已知$\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sin C = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{2} \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\cos B$，代入得$\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{2}}{2} = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{2} \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\cos B$，\\\\\\\\n解得$\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\cos B = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{1}{2}$，\\\\\\\\n而$B \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\in (0,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\pi)$，故$B = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\pi}{3}$。\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n【小问2详解】\\\\\\\\n由（1）知$\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\cos C = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{2}}{2}$，$\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sin C = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{2}}{2}$，故$C = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\pi}{4}$，\\\\\\\\n则$A = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\pi - B - C = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\pi - \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\pi}{3} - \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\pi}{4} = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{5\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\pi}{12}$，\\\\\\\\n由正弦定理：$\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{a}{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sin A} = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{b}{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sin B} = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{c}{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sin C} = 2R$，\\\\\\\\n得$a = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{c \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sin A}{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sin C} = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{c \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sin \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{5\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\pi}{12}}{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{2}}{2}} = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{2} c \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sin \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{5\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\pi}{12}$，\\\\\\\\n$b = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{c \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sin B}{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sin C} = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{c \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\cdot \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{3}}{2}}{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{2}}{2}} = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{3}}{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{2}} c = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{6}}{2} c$，\\\\\\\\n又$\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sin \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{5\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\pi}{12} = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sin\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\left(\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\pi}{4} + \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\pi}{6}\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\right) = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sin\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\pi}{4}\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\cos\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\pi}{6} + \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\cos\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\pi}{4}\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sin\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\pi}{6} = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{2}}{2} \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\cdot \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{3}}{2} + \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{2}}{2} \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\cdot \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{1}{2} = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{6} + \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{2}}{4}$，\\\\\\\\n所以$a = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{2} c \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\cdot \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{6} + \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{2}}{4} = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{c(\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{12} + \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{4})}{4} = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{c(2\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{3} + 2)}{4} = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{c(\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{3} + 1)}{2}$，\\\\\\\\n三角形面积$S = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{1}{2} ab \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sin C = 3 + \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{3}$，\\\\\\\\n代入得：\\\\\\\\n$$\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{1}{2} \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\cdot \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{c(\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{3} + 1)}{2} \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\cdot \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{6}}{2} c \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\cdot \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{2}}{2} = 3 + \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{3}\\\\\\\\n$$\\\\\\\\n化简：\\\\\\\\n$$\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{c^2 (\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{3} + 1) \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{6} \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{2}}{16} = 3 + \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{3}\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\Rightarrow \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{c^2 (\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{3} + 1) \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\cdot \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{12}}{16} = 3 + \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{3}\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\Rightarrow \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{c^2 (\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{3} + 1) \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\cdot 2\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{3}}{16} = 3 + \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{3}\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\Rightarrow \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{c^2 (3 + \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{3})}{8} = 3 + \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{3}\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\Rightarrow c^2 = 8 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\Rightarrow c = 2\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{2}\\\\\\\\n$$\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"comment\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"本题综合考查正弦定理、余弦定理及三角恒等变换，需熟练掌握三角函数值与角度的对应关系，以及和角公式的应用。第二问计算较繁，注意化简技巧。\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"knowledge_points\\\\\\\": [\\\\\\\"余弦定理\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"正弦定理\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"三角形面积公式\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"三角恒等变换\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"特殊角的三角函数值\\\\\\\"],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"difficulty\\\\\\\": 4,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"bbox\\\\\\\": [87, 275, 842, 465],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"region_json\\\\\\\": {\\\\\\\"x1\\\\\\\": 87, \\\\\\\"y1\\\\\\\": 275, \\\\\\\"x2\\\\\\\": 842, \\\\\\\"y2\\\\\\\": 465},\\\\n      \\\\\\\"confidence\\\\\\\": 0.98,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"images\\\\\\\": [],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"page_end\\\\\\\": 12,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"need_review_reason\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"raw_explanation\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"【答案】（1）$B = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\pi}{3}$\\\\\\\\n（2）$2\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{2}$\\\\\\\"\\\\n    }\\\\n  ]\\\\n}\\\", \\\"reasoning_content\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"role\\\": \\\"assistant\\\"}, \\\"finish_reason\\\": \\\"stop\\\", \\\"index\\\": 0, \\\"logprobs\\\": null}], \\\"object\\\": \\\"chat.completion\\\", \\\"usage\\\": {\\\"prompt_tokens\\\": 3583, \\\"completion_tokens\\\": 1658, \\\"total_tokens\\\": 5241, \\\"completion_tokens_details\\\": {\\\"text_tokens\\\": 1658}, \\\"prompt_tokens_details\\\": {\\\"image_tokens\\\": 2522, \\\"text_tokens\\\": 1061, \\\"cached_tokens\\\": 0}}, \\\"created\\\": 1778252086, \\\"system_fingerprint\\\": null, \\\"model\\\": \\\"qwen3-vl-plus\\\", \\\"id\\\": \\\"chatcmpl-d335d6b9-62ef-9673-8e88-002858316749\\\"}\"', '{\n  \"page_no\": 12,\n  \"questions\": [\n    {\n      \"question_no\": \"15\",\n      \"section_title\": \"四、解答题\",\n      \"question_type\": \"computation\",\n      \"stem\": \"记△ABC内角A、B、C的对边分别为a，b，c，已知$\\\\sin C = \\\\sqrt{2} \\\\cos B$，$a^2 + b^2 - c^2 = \\\\sqrt{2}ab$。（1）求B；（2）若△ABC的面积为$3+\\\\sqrt{3}$，求c。\",\n      \"options\": [],\n      \"answer\": \"(1) $B = \\\\frac{\\\\pi}{3}$\\n(2) $2\\\\sqrt{2}$\",\n      \"analysis\": \"【点睛】关键点点睛：本题的关键在于将问题转化为随机变量问题，利用期望的可加性得到等量关系，从而避免繁琐的列举。\",\n      \"solution\": \"【解析】\\n【分析】（1）由余弦定理、平方关系依次求出$\\\\cos C, \\\\sin C$，最后结合已知$\\\\sin C = \\\\sqrt{2} \\\\cos B$得$\\\\cos B$的值即可；\\n（2）首先求出$A,B,C$，然后由正弦定理可将$a,b$均用含有$c$的式子表示，结合三角形面积公式即可列方程求解。\\n\\n【小问1详解】\\n由余弦定理有$a^2 + b^2 - c^2 = 2ab\\\\cos C$，对比已知$a^2 + b^2 - c^2 = \\\\sqrt{2}ab$，\\n可得$\\\\cos C = \\\\frac{a^2 + b^2 - c^2}{2ab} = \\\\frac{\\\\sqrt{2}ab}{2ab} = \\\\frac{\\\\sqrt{2}}{2}$，\\n因为$C \\\\in (0,\\\\pi)$，所以$\\\\sin C > 0$，\\n故$\\\\sin C = \\\\sqrt{1 - \\\\cos^2 C} = \\\\sqrt{1 - \\\\left(\\\\frac{\\\\sqrt{2}}{2}\\\\right)^2} = \\\\frac{\\\\sqrt{2}}{2}$，\\n又已知$\\\\sin C = \\\\sqrt{2} \\\\cos B$，代入得$\\\\frac{\\\\sqrt{2}}{2} = \\\\sqrt{2} \\\\cos B$，\\n解得$\\\\cos B = \\\\frac{1}{2}$，\\n而$B \\\\in (0,\\\\pi)$，故$B = \\\\frac{\\\\pi}{3}$。\\n\\n【小问2详解】\\n由（1）知$\\\\cos C = \\\\frac{\\\\sqrt{2}}{2}$，$\\\\sin C = \\\\frac{\\\\sqrt{2}}{2}$，故$C = \\\\frac{\\\\pi}{4}$，\\n则$A = \\\\pi - B - C = \\\\pi - \\\\frac{\\\\pi}{3} - \\\\frac{\\\\pi}{4} = \\\\frac{5\\\\pi}{12}$，\\n由正弦定理：$\\\\frac{a}{\\\\sin A} = \\\\frac{b}{\\\\sin B} = \\\\frac{c}{\\\\sin C} = 2R$，\\n得$a = \\\\frac{c \\\\sin A}{\\\\sin C} = \\\\frac{c \\\\sin \\\\frac{5\\\\pi}{12}}{\\\\frac{\\\\sqrt{2}}{2}} = \\\\sqrt{2} c \\\\sin \\\\frac{5\\\\pi}{12}$，\\n$b = \\\\frac{c \\\\sin B}{\\\\sin C} = \\\\frac{c \\\\cdot \\\\frac{\\\\sqrt{3}}{2}}{\\\\frac{\\\\sqrt{2}}{2}} = \\\\frac{\\\\sqrt{3}}{\\\\sqrt{2}} c = \\\\frac{\\\\sqrt{6}}{2} c$，\\n又$\\\\sin \\\\frac{5\\\\pi}{12} = \\\\sin\\\\left(\\\\frac{\\\\pi}{4} + \\\\frac{\\\\pi}{6}\\\\right) = \\\\sin\\\\frac{\\\\pi}{4}\\\\cos\\\\frac{\\\\pi}{6} + \\\\cos\\\\frac{\\\\pi}{4}\\\\sin\\\\frac{\\\\pi}{6} = \\\\frac{\\\\sqrt{2}}{2} \\\\cdot \\\\frac{\\\\sqrt{3}}{2} + \\\\frac{\\\\sqrt{2}}{2} \\\\cdot \\\\frac{1}{2} = \\\\frac{\\\\sqrt{6} + \\\\sqrt{2}}{4}$，\\n所以$a = \\\\sqrt{2} c \\\\cdot \\\\frac{\\\\sqrt{6} + \\\\sqrt{2}}{4} = \\\\frac{c(\\\\sqrt{12} + \\\\sqrt{4})}{4} = \\\\frac{c(2\\\\sqrt{3} + 2)}{4} = \\\\frac{c(\\\\sqrt{3} + 1)}{2}$，\\n三角形面积$S = \\\\frac{1}{2} ab \\\\sin C = 3 + \\\\sqrt{3}$，\\n代入得：\\n$$\\n\\\\frac{1}{2} \\\\cdot \\\\frac{c(\\\\sqrt{3} + 1)}{2} \\\\cdot \\\\frac{\\\\sqrt{6}}{2} c \\\\cdot \\\\frac{\\\\sqrt{2}}{2} = 3 + \\\\sqrt{3}\\n$$\\n化简：\\n$$\\n\\\\frac{c^2 (\\\\sqrt{3} + 1) \\\\sqrt{6} \\\\sqrt{2}}{16} = 3 + \\\\sqrt{3}\\n\\\\Rightarrow \\\\frac{c^2 (\\\\sqrt{3} + 1) \\\\cdot \\\\sqrt{12}}{16} = 3 + \\\\sqrt{3}\\n\\\\Rightarrow \\\\frac{c^2 (\\\\sqrt{3} + 1) \\\\cdot 2\\\\sqrt{3}}{16} = 3 + \\\\sqrt{3}\\n\\\\Rightarrow \\\\frac{c^2 (3 + \\\\sqrt{3})}{8} = 3 + \\\\sqrt{3}\\n\\\\Rightarrow c^2 = 8 \\\\Rightarrow c = 2\\\\sqrt{2}\\n$$\",\n      \"comment\": \"本题综合考查正弦定理、余弦定理及三角恒等变换，需熟练掌握三角函数值与角度的对应关系，以及和角公式的应用。第二问计算较繁，注意化简技巧。\",\n      \"knowledge_points\": [\"余弦定理\", \"正弦定理\", \"三角形面积公式\", \"三角恒等变换\", \"特殊角的三角函数值\"],\n      \"difficulty\": 4,\n      \"bbox\": [87, 275, 842, 465],\n      \"region_json\": {\"x1\": 87, \"y1\": 275, \"x2\": 842, \"y2\": 465},\n      \"confidence\": 0.98,\n      \"images\": [],\n      \"page_end\": 12,\n      \"need_review_reason\": \"\",\n      \"raw_explanation\": \"【答案】（1）$B = \\\\frac{\\\\pi}{3}$\\n（2）$2\\\\sqrt{2}$\"\n    }\n  ]\n}', 1, NULL, 49328, '2026-05-08 14:54:46.222729', 1, 45, NULL);
INSERT INTO `tiku_ai_parse_result` VALUES (46, 'qwen3-vl-plus', NULL, NULL, '\"{\\\"choices\\\": [{\\\"message\\\": {\\\"content\\\": \\\"{\\\\n  \\\\\\\"page_no\\\\\\\": 13,\\\\n  \\\\\\\"questions\\\\\\\": [\\\\n    {\\\\n      \\\\\\\"question_no\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"16\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"section_title\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"question_type\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"computation\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"stem\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"16. 已知 $A(0,3)$ 和 $P\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\left(3,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{3}{2}\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\right)$ 为椭圆 $C:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{x^2}{a^2}+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{y^2}{b^2}=1(a>b>0)$ 上两点.\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n（1）求 $C$ 的离心率；\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"options\\\\\\\": [],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"answer\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"analysis\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"solution\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"comment\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"knowledge_points\\\\\\\": [\\\\\\\"椭圆的标准方程\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"点在椭圆上的条件\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"离心率计算\\\\\\\"],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"difficulty\\\\\\\": 3,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"bbox\\\\\\\": [87, 820, 624, 900],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"region_json\\\\\\\": {\\\\\\\"x1\\\\\\\": 87, \\\\\\\"y1\\\\\\\": 820, \\\\\\\"x2\\\\\\\": 624, \\\\\\\"y2\\\\\\\": 900},\\\\n      \\\\\\\"confidence\\\\\\\": 0.98,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"images\\\\\\\": [],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"page_end\\\\\\\": 13,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"need_review_reason\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"raw_explanation\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n    }\\\\n  ]\\\\n}\\\", \\\"reasoning_content\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"role\\\": \\\"assistant\\\"}, \\\"finish_reason\\\": \\\"stop\\\", \\\"index\\\": 0, \\\"logprobs\\\": null}], \\\"object\\\": \\\"chat.completion\\\", \\\"usage\\\": {\\\"prompt_tokens\\\": 3583, \\\"completion_tokens\\\": 293, \\\"total_tokens\\\": 3876, \\\"completion_tokens_details\\\": {\\\"text_tokens\\\": 293}, \\\"prompt_tokens_details\\\": {\\\"image_tokens\\\": 2522, \\\"text_tokens\\\": 1061, \\\"cached_tokens\\\": 0}}, \\\"created\\\": 1778252104, \\\"system_fingerprint\\\": null, \\\"model\\\": \\\"qwen3-vl-plus\\\", \\\"id\\\": \\\"chatcmpl-fd727861-32da-9ce1-85f8-cdb8d9fa3378\\\"}\"', '{\n  \"page_no\": 13,\n  \"questions\": [\n    {\n      \"question_no\": \"16\",\n      \"section_title\": \"\",\n      \"question_type\": \"computation\",\n      \"stem\": \"16. 已知 $A(0,3)$ 和 $P\\\\left(3,\\\\frac{3}{2}\\\\right)$ 为椭圆 $C:\\\\frac{x^2}{a^2}+\\\\frac{y^2}{b^2}=1(a>b>0)$ 上两点.\\n\\n（1）求 $C$ 的离心率；\",\n      \"options\": [],\n      \"answer\": \"\",\n      \"analysis\": \"\",\n      \"solution\": \"\",\n      \"comment\": \"\",\n      \"knowledge_points\": [\"椭圆的标准方程\", \"点在椭圆上的条件\", \"离心率计算\"],\n      \"difficulty\": 3,\n      \"bbox\": [87, 820, 624, 900],\n      \"region_json\": {\"x1\": 87, \"y1\": 820, \"x2\": 624, \"y2\": 900},\n      \"confidence\": 0.98,\n      \"images\": [],\n      \"page_end\": 13,\n      \"need_review_reason\": \"\",\n      \"raw_explanation\": \"\"\n    }\n  ]\n}', 1, NULL, 17994, '2026-05-08 14:55:04.263800', 1, 46, NULL);
INSERT INTO `tiku_ai_parse_result` VALUES (47, 'qwen3-vl-plus', NULL, NULL, '\"{\\\"choices\\\": [{\\\"message\\\": {\\\"content\\\": \\\"{\\\\n  \\\\\\\"page_no\\\\\\\": 14,\\\\n  \\\\\\\"questions\\\\\\\": [\\\\n    {\\\\n      \\\\\\\"question_no\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"2\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"section_title\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"question_type\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"computation\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"stem\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"（2）若过 P 的直线 l 交 C 于另一点 B，且 △ABP 的面积为 9，求 l 的方程.\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"options\\\\\\\": [],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"answer\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"3x - 2y - 6 = 0 或 x - 2y = 0\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"analysis\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"（1）代入两点得到关于 a,b 的方程，解出即可；（2）方法一：以 |AP| 为底，求出三角形的高，即点 B 到直线 AP 的距离，再利用平行线距离公式得到平移后的直线方程，联立椭圆方程得到 B 点坐标，则得到直线 l 的方程；方法二：同法一得到点 B 到直线 AP 的距离，再设 B(x₀, y₀)，根据点到直线距离和点在椭圆上得到方程组，解出即可；法三：同法一得到点 B 到直线 AP 的距离，利用椭圆的参数方程即可求解；法四：首先验证直线 AB 斜率不存在的情况，再设直线 y = kx + 3，联立椭圆方程，得到点 B 坐标，再利用点到直线距离公式即可；法五：首先考虑直线 PB 斜率不存在的情况，再设 PB: y - 3/2 = k(x - 3)，利用弦长公式和点到直线的距离公式即可得到答案；法六：设线法与法五一致，利用水平宽乘铅锤高乘 1/2 表达面积即可。\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"solution\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"【小问1详解】由题意得 { b = 3; 9/a² + 4/b² = 1 }，解得 { b² = 9; a² = 12 }，所以 e = √(1 - b²/a²) = √(1 - 9/12) = 1/2。【小问2详解】法一：k_AP = (3 - 3/2)/(0 - 3) = -1/2，则直线 AP 的方程为 y = -1/2 x + 3，即 x + 2y - 6 = 0。\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"comment\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"knowledge_points\\\\\\\": [\\\\\\\"椭圆标准方程\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"直线与椭圆位置关系\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"点到直线距离公式\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"三角形面积公式\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"斜率计算\\\\\\\"],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"difficulty\\\\\\\": 4,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"bbox\\\\\\\": [95, 54, 910, 870],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"region_json\\\\\\\": {\\\\n        \\\\\\\"x1\\\\\\\": 0,\\\\n        \\\\\\\"y1\\\\\\\": 0,\\\\n        \\\\\\\"x2\\\\\\\": 1000,\\\\n        \\\\\\\"y2\\\\\\\": 2000\\\\n      },\\\\n      \\\\\\\"confidence\\\\\\\": 0.98,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"images\\\\\\\": [],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"page_end\\\\\\\": 14,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"need_review_reason\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"raw_explanation\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n    }\\\\n  ]\\\\n}\\\", \\\"reasoning_content\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"role\\\": \\\"assistant\\\"}, \\\"finish_reason\\\": \\\"stop\\\", \\\"index\\\": 0, \\\"logprobs\\\": null}], \\\"object\\\": \\\"chat.completion\\\", \\\"usage\\\": {\\\"prompt_tokens\\\": 3583, \\\"completion_tokens\\\": 698, \\\"total_tokens\\\": 4281, \\\"completion_tokens_details\\\": {\\\"text_tokens\\\": 698}, \\\"prompt_tokens_details\\\": {\\\"image_tokens\\\": 2522, \\\"text_tokens\\\": 1061, \\\"cached_tokens\\\": 0}}, \\\"created\\\": 1778252129, \\\"system_fingerprint\\\": null, \\\"model\\\": \\\"qwen3-vl-plus\\\", \\\"id\\\": \\\"chatcmpl-58b2ecad-8ff8-9106-80ed-67f4c05e1ffa\\\"}\"', '{\n  \"page_no\": 14,\n  \"questions\": [\n    {\n      \"question_no\": \"2\",\n      \"section_title\": \"\",\n      \"question_type\": \"computation\",\n      \"stem\": \"（2）若过 P 的直线 l 交 C 于另一点 B，且 △ABP 的面积为 9，求 l 的方程.\",\n      \"options\": [],\n      \"answer\": \"3x - 2y - 6 = 0 或 x - 2y = 0\",\n      \"analysis\": \"（1）代入两点得到关于 a,b 的方程，解出即可；（2）方法一：以 |AP| 为底，求出三角形的高，即点 B 到直线 AP 的距离，再利用平行线距离公式得到平移后的直线方程，联立椭圆方程得到 B 点坐标，则得到直线 l 的方程；方法二：同法一得到点 B 到直线 AP 的距离，再设 B(x₀, y₀)，根据点到直线距离和点在椭圆上得到方程组，解出即可；法三：同法一得到点 B 到直线 AP 的距离，利用椭圆的参数方程即可求解；法四：首先验证直线 AB 斜率不存在的情况，再设直线 y = kx + 3，联立椭圆方程，得到点 B 坐标，再利用点到直线距离公式即可；法五：首先考虑直线 PB 斜率不存在的情况，再设 PB: y - 3/2 = k(x - 3)，利用弦长公式和点到直线的距离公式即可得到答案；法六：设线法与法五一致，利用水平宽乘铅锤高乘 1/2 表达面积即可。\",\n      \"solution\": \"【小问1详解】由题意得 { b = 3; 9/a² + 4/b² = 1 }，解得 { b² = 9; a² = 12 }，所以 e = √(1 - b²/a²) = √(1 - 9/12) = 1/2。【小问2详解】法一：k_AP = (3 - 3/2)/(0 - 3) = -1/2，则直线 AP 的方程为 y = -1/2 x + 3，即 x + 2y - 6 = 0。\",\n      \"comment\": \"\",\n      \"knowledge_points\": [\"椭圆标准方程\", \"直线与椭圆位置关系\", \"点到直线距离公式\", \"三角形面积公式\", \"斜率计算\"],\n      \"difficulty\": 4,\n      \"bbox\": [95, 54, 910, 870],\n      \"region_json\": {\n        \"x1\": 0,\n        \"y1\": 0,\n        \"x2\": 1000,\n        \"y2\": 2000\n      },\n      \"confidence\": 0.98,\n      \"images\": [],\n      \"page_end\": 14,\n      \"need_review_reason\": \"\",\n      \"raw_explanation\": \"\"\n    }\n  ]\n}', 1, NULL, 24636, '2026-05-08 14:55:28.932520', 1, 47, NULL);
INSERT INTO `tiku_ai_parse_result` VALUES (48, 'qwen3-vl-plus', NULL, NULL, '\"{\\\"choices\\\": [{\\\"message\\\": {\\\"content\\\": \\\"{\\\\n  \\\\\\\"page_no\\\\\\\": 15,\\\\n  \\\\\\\"questions\\\\\\\": [\\\\n    {\\\\n      \\\\\\\"question_no\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"未编号\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"section_title\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"question_type\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"computation\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"stem\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"已知点 $P(3, \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{3}{2})$，计算 $|AP| = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{(0-3)^2 + \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\left(3 - \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{3}{2}\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\right)^2} = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{3\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{5}}{2}$，由（1）知椭圆 $C: \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{x^2}{12} + \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{y^2}{9} = 1$。设点 $B$ 到直线 $AP$ 的距离为 $d$，则 $d = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{2 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\times 9}{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{3\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{5}}{2}} = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{12\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{5}}{5}$。将直线 $AP$ 沿着与 $AP$ 垂直的方向平移 $\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{12\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{5}}{5}$ 单位即可，此时该平行线与椭圆的交点即为点 $B$。设该平行线方程为：$x + 2y + C = 0$，则 $\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{|C + 6|}{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{5}} = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{12\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{5}}{5}$，解得 $C = 6$ 或 $C = -18$。当 $C = 6$ 时，联立 $\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\begin{cases} \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{x^2}{12} + \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{y^2}{9} = 1 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ x + 2y + 6 = 0 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\end{cases}$，解得 $\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\begin{cases} x = 0 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ y = -3 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\end{cases}$ 或 $\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\begin{cases} x = -3 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ y = -\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{3}{2} \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\end{cases}$，即 $B(0, -3)$ 或 $\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\left(-3, -\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{3}{2}\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\right)$。当 $B(0, -3)$ 时，此时 $k_l = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{3}{2}$，直线 $l$ 的方程为 $y = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{3}{2}x - 3$，即 $3x - 2y - 6 = 0$；当 $B\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\left(-3, -\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{3}{2}\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\right)$ 时，此时 $k_l = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{1}{2}$，直线 $l$ 的方程为 $y = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{1}{2}x$，即 $x - 2y = 0$。当 $C = -18$ 时，联立 $\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\begin{cases} \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{x^2}{12} + \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{y^2}{9} = 1 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ x + 2y - 18 = 0 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\end{cases}$ 得 $2y^2 - 27y + 117 = 0$，判别式 $\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\Delta = 27^2 - 4 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\times 2 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\times 117 = -207 < 0$，此时该直线与椭圆无交点。综上直线 $l$ 的方程为 $3x - 2y - 6 = 0$ 或 $x - 2y = 0$。法二：同法一得到直线 $AP$ 的方程为 $x + 2y - 6 = 0$。\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"options\\\\\\\": [],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"answer\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"3x - 2y - 6 = 0 或 x - 2y = 0\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"analysis\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"本题考查椭圆与直线的位置关系、点到直线的距离公式、直线平移及联立方程求交点。通过设定与AP平行的直线方程，利用点到直线距离等于已知值，求出参数C，再联立椭圆方程判断交点存在性，最终确定满足条件的点B，进而求出所求直线l的方程。\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"solution\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"1. 计算 |AP| = 3√5/2；\\\\\\\\n2. 由面积法或几何关系得点B到AP的距离 d = 12√5/5；\\\\\\\\n3. 设平行线为 x + 2y + C = 0，由距离公式得 |C+6|/√5 = 12√5/5 ⇒ C = 6 或 -18；\\\\\\\\n4. C=6 时，联立椭圆与直线得两交点 B(0,-3) 和 (-3,-3/2)，对应斜率分别为 3/2 和 1/2，得直线 l 方程为 3x−2y−6=0 或 x−2y=0；\\\\\\\\n5. C=−18 时，判别式 Δ<0，无实交点，舍去；\\\\\\\\n6. 综上得所求直线方程。\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"comment\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"本题综合性强，涉及解析几何多个核心知识点，需熟练掌握距离公式、直线与椭圆位置关系判定及代数运算能力。法二提示可先求AP方程，思路更清晰。\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"knowledge_points\\\\\\\": [\\\\\\\"椭圆标准方程\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"点到直线距离公式\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"直线平行与平移\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"直线与椭圆位置关系\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"联立方程求解\\\\\\\"],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"difficulty\\\\\\\": 4,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"bbox\\\\\\\": [85, 55, 695, 885],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"region_json\\\\\\\": {\\\\\\\"x1\\\\\\\": 85, \\\\\\\"y1\\\\\\\": 55, \\\\\\\"x2\\\\\\\": 695, \\\\\\\"y2\\\\\\\": 885},\\\\n      \\\\\\\"confidence\\\\\\\": 0.98,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"images\\\\\\\": [],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"page_end\\\\\\\": 15,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"need_review_reason\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"raw_explanation\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n    }\\\\n  ]\\\\n}\\\", \\\"reasoning_content\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"role\\\": \\\"assistant\\\"}, \\\"finish_reason\\\": \\\"stop\\\", \\\"index\\\": 0, \\\"logprobs\\\": null}], \\\"object\\\": \\\"chat.completion\\\", \\\"usage\\\": {\\\"prompt_tokens\\\": 3583, \\\"completion_tokens\\\": 1321, \\\"total_tokens\\\": 4904, \\\"completion_tokens_details\\\": {\\\"text_tokens\\\": 1321}, \\\"prompt_tokens_details\\\": {\\\"image_tokens\\\": 2522, \\\"text_tokens\\\": 1061, \\\"cached_tokens\\\": 0}}, \\\"created\\\": 1778252166, \\\"system_fingerprint\\\": null, \\\"model\\\": \\\"qwen3-vl-plus\\\", \\\"id\\\": \\\"chatcmpl-33dc7371-4365-92f5-bbbc-6b83566cd451\\\"}\"', '{\n  \"page_no\": 15,\n  \"questions\": [\n    {\n      \"question_no\": \"未编号\",\n      \"section_title\": \"\",\n      \"question_type\": \"computation\",\n      \"stem\": \"已知点 $P(3, \\\\frac{3}{2})$，计算 $|AP| = \\\\sqrt{(0-3)^2 + \\\\left(3 - \\\\frac{3}{2}\\\\right)^2} = \\\\frac{3\\\\sqrt{5}}{2}$，由（1）知椭圆 $C: \\\\frac{x^2}{12} + \\\\frac{y^2}{9} = 1$。设点 $B$ 到直线 $AP$ 的距离为 $d$，则 $d = \\\\frac{2 \\\\times 9}{\\\\frac{3\\\\sqrt{5}}{2}} = \\\\frac{12\\\\sqrt{5}}{5}$。将直线 $AP$ 沿着与 $AP$ 垂直的方向平移 $\\\\frac{12\\\\sqrt{5}}{5}$ 单位即可，此时该平行线与椭圆的交点即为点 $B$。设该平行线方程为：$x + 2y + C = 0$，则 $\\\\frac{|C + 6|}{\\\\sqrt{5}} = \\\\frac{12\\\\sqrt{5}}{5}$，解得 $C = 6$ 或 $C = -18$。当 $C = 6$ 时，联立 $\\\\begin{cases} \\\\frac{x^2}{12} + \\\\frac{y^2}{9} = 1 \\\\\\\\ x + 2y + 6 = 0 \\\\end{cases}$，解得 $\\\\begin{cases} x = 0 \\\\\\\\ y = -3 \\\\end{cases}$ 或 $\\\\begin{cases} x = -3 \\\\\\\\ y = -\\\\frac{3}{2} \\\\end{cases}$，即 $B(0, -3)$ 或 $\\\\left(-3, -\\\\frac{3}{2}\\\\right)$。当 $B(0, -3)$ 时，此时 $k_l = \\\\frac{3}{2}$，直线 $l$ 的方程为 $y = \\\\frac{3}{2}x - 3$，即 $3x - 2y - 6 = 0$；当 $B\\\\left(-3, -\\\\frac{3}{2}\\\\right)$ 时，此时 $k_l = \\\\frac{1}{2}$，直线 $l$ 的方程为 $y = \\\\frac{1}{2}x$，即 $x - 2y = 0$。当 $C = -18$ 时，联立 $\\\\begin{cases} \\\\frac{x^2}{12} + \\\\frac{y^2}{9} = 1 \\\\\\\\ x + 2y - 18 = 0 \\\\end{cases}$ 得 $2y^2 - 27y + 117 = 0$，判别式 $\\\\Delta = 27^2 - 4 \\\\times 2 \\\\times 117 = -207 < 0$，此时该直线与椭圆无交点。综上直线 $l$ 的方程为 $3x - 2y - 6 = 0$ 或 $x - 2y = 0$。法二：同法一得到直线 $AP$ 的方程为 $x + 2y - 6 = 0$。\",\n      \"options\": [],\n      \"answer\": \"3x - 2y - 6 = 0 或 x - 2y = 0\",\n      \"analysis\": \"本题考查椭圆与直线的位置关系、点到直线的距离公式、直线平移及联立方程求交点。通过设定与AP平行的直线方程，利用点到直线距离等于已知值，求出参数C，再联立椭圆方程判断交点存在性，最终确定满足条件的点B，进而求出所求直线l的方程。\",\n      \"solution\": \"1. 计算 |AP| = 3√5/2；\\n2. 由面积法或几何关系得点B到AP的距离 d = 12√5/5；\\n3. 设平行线为 x + 2y + C = 0，由距离公式得 |C+6|/√5 = 12√5/5 ⇒ C = 6 或 -18；\\n4. C=6 时，联立椭圆与直线得两交点 B(0,-3) 和 (-3,-3/2)，对应斜率分别为 3/2 和 1/2，得直线 l 方程为 3x−2y−6=0 或 x−2y=0；\\n5. C=−18 时，判别式 Δ<0，无实交点，舍去；\\n6. 综上得所求直线方程。\",\n      \"comment\": \"本题综合性强，涉及解析几何多个核心知识点，需熟练掌握距离公式、直线与椭圆位置关系判定及代数运算能力。法二提示可先求AP方程，思路更清晰。\",\n      \"knowledge_points\": [\"椭圆标准方程\", \"点到直线距离公式\", \"直线平行与平移\", \"直线与椭圆位置关系\", \"联立方程求解\"],\n      \"difficulty\": 4,\n      \"bbox\": [85, 55, 695, 885],\n      \"region_json\": {\"x1\": 85, \"y1\": 55, \"x2\": 695, \"y2\": 885},\n      \"confidence\": 0.98,\n      \"images\": [],\n      \"page_end\": 15,\n      \"need_review_reason\": \"\",\n      \"raw_explanation\": \"\"\n    }\n  ]\n}', 1, NULL, 37253, '2026-05-08 14:56:06.220916', 1, 48, NULL);
INSERT INTO `tiku_ai_parse_result` VALUES (49, 'qwen3-vl-plus', NULL, NULL, '\"{\\\"choices\\\": [{\\\"message\\\": {\\\"content\\\": \\\"{\\\\n  \\\\\\\"page_no\\\\\\\": 16,\\\\n  \\\\\\\"questions\\\\\\\": [\\\\n    {\\\\n      \\\\\\\"question_no\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"未编号\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"section_title\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"question_type\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"computation\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"stem\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"点B到直线AP的距离d=12√5/5，设B(x₀,y₀)，则{|x₀+2y₀−6|/√5=12√5/5, x₀²/12+y₀²/9=1}，解得{x₀=−3, y₀=−3/2}或{x₀=0, y₀=−3}，即B(0,−3)或(−3,−3/2)，以下同法一。\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"options\\\\\\\": [],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"answer\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"B(0,−3)或(−3,−3/2)\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"analysis\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"本题通过点到直线距离公式与椭圆方程联立求解点B坐标，属于解析几何中典型的代数方法求交点问题。\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"solution\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"由点B在椭圆x²/12 + y²/9 = 1上，且到直线AP（方程为x+2y−6=0）的距离为12√5/5，利用点到直线距离公式列方程，联立椭圆方程，解得两组解：(x₀, y₀) = (−3, −3/2) 或 (0, −3)。\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"comment\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"本题考查点到直线距离公式、椭圆标准方程及方程组求解能力，计算需注意绝对值的分情况讨论。\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"knowledge_points\\\\\\\": [\\\\\\\"点到直线距离公式\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"椭圆标准方程\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"方程组求解\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"绝对值方程\\\\\\\"],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"difficulty\\\\\\\": 4,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"bbox\\\\\\\": [85, 55, 640, 260],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"region_json\\\\\\\": {\\\\\\\"x1\\\\\\\": 0, \\\\\\\"y1\\\\\\\": 0, \\\\\\\"x2\\\\\\\": 1000, \\\\\\\"y2\\\\\\\": 2000},\\\\n      \\\\\\\"confidence\\\\\\\": 0.98,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"images\\\\\\\": [],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"page_end\\\\\\\": 16,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"need_review_reason\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"raw_explanation\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n    },\\\\n    {\\\\n      \\\\\\\"question_no\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"未编号\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"section_title\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"question_type\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"computation\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"stem\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"法三：同法一得到直线AP的方程为x+2y−6=0，点B到直线AP的距离d=12√5/5，设B(2√3 cosθ, 3 sinθ)，其中θ∈[0,2π)，则有|2√3 cosθ+6 sinθ−6|/√5=12√5/5，联立cos²θ+sin²θ=1，解得{cosθ=−√3/2, sinθ=−1/2}或{cosθ=0, sinθ=−1}，即B(0,−3)或(−3,−3/2)，以下同法一；\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"options\\\\\\\": [],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"answer\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"B(0,−3)或(−3,−3/2)\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"analysis\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"本题采用参数方程法（椭圆的三角参数化）求解点B坐标，将几何条件转化为三角恒等式求解。\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"solution\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"设B点坐标为椭圆参数形式(2√3 cosθ, 3 sinθ)，代入点到直线距离公式，化简得|2√3 cosθ + 6 sinθ − 6| = 12，结合cos²θ + sin²θ = 1，解得两组三角函数值，对应两点坐标。\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"comment\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"参数法是处理椭圆上动点问题的有效手段，可避免二次方程判别式复杂性，但需熟练掌握三角恒等变换。\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"knowledge_points\\\\\\\": [\\\\\\\"椭圆参数方程\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"三角恒等式\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"点到直线距离公式\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"三角方程求解\\\\\\\"],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"difficulty\\\\\\\": 4,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"bbox\\\\\\\": [85, 285, 725, 600],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"region_json\\\\\\\": {\\\\\\\"x1\\\\\\\": 0, \\\\\\\"y1\\\\\\\": 0, \\\\\\\"x2\\\\\\\": 1000, \\\\\\\"y2\\\\\\\": 2000},\\\\n      \\\\\\\"confidence\\\\\\\": 0.97,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"images\\\\\\\": [],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"page_end\\\\\\\": 16,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"need_review_reason\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"raw_explanation\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n    },\\\\n    {\\\\n      \\\\\\\"question_no\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"未编号\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"section_title\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"question_type\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"computation\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"stem\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"法四：当直线AB的斜率不存在时，此时B(0,−3)，S△PAB=1/2×6×3=9，符合题意，此时k_l=3/2，直线l的方程为y=3/2 x−3，即3x−2y−6=0；当直线AB的斜率存在时，设直线AB的方程为y=kx+3，联立椭圆方程有{x²/12+y²/9=1}，则(4k²+3)x²+24kx=0，其中k≠k_AP，即k≠−1/2，\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"options\\\\\\\": [],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"answer\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"直线l的方程为3x−2y−6=0 或 (4k²+3)x²+24kx=0（k≠−1/2）\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"analysis\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"本题分斜率存在与不存在两种情况讨论，结合三角形面积条件与椭圆联立，推导直线方程。\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"solution\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"先考虑AB垂直x轴（斜率不存在），得B(0,−3)，验证面积S△PAB=9成立，进而求出直线l斜率为3/2，得方程3x−2y−6=0；再设AB斜率为k，联立椭圆方程消元后得关于x的二次方程(4k²+3)x²+24kx=0，并排除k=−1/2（与AP平行）的情况。\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"comment\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"分类讨论思想在解析几何中至关重要，尤其涉及斜率是否存在、直线是否过定点等问题时必须严谨。\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"knowledge_points\\\\\\\": [\\\\\\\"直线斜率分类讨论\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"三角形面积公式\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"直线与椭圆联立方程\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"参数限制条件\\\\\\\"],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"difficulty\\\\\\\": 5,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"bbox\\\\\\\": [85, 625, 835, 845],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"region_json\\\\\\\": {\\\\\\\"x1\\\\\\\": 0, \\\\\\\"y1\\\\\\\": 0, \\\\\\\"x2\\\\\\\": 1000, \\\\\\\"y2\\\\\\\": 2000},\\\\n      \\\\\\\"confidence\\\\\\\": 0.96,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"images\\\\\\\": [],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"page_end\\\\\\\": 16,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"need_review_reason\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"raw_explanation\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n    }\\\\n  ]\\\\n}\\\", \\\"reasoning_content\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"role\\\": \\\"assistant\\\"}, \\\"finish_reason\\\": \\\"stop\\\", \\\"index\\\": 0, \\\"logprobs\\\": null}], \\\"object\\\": \\\"chat.completion\\\", \\\"usage\\\": {\\\"prompt_tokens\\\": 3583, \\\"completion_tokens\\\": 1558, \\\"total_tokens\\\": 5141, \\\"completion_tokens_details\\\": {\\\"text_tokens\\\": 1558}, \\\"prompt_tokens_details\\\": {\\\"image_tokens\\\": 2522, \\\"text_tokens\\\": 1061, \\\"cached_tokens\\\": 0}}, \\\"created\\\": 1778252214, \\\"system_fingerprint\\\": null, \\\"model\\\": \\\"qwen3-vl-plus\\\", \\\"id\\\": \\\"chatcmpl-64d10393-e01d-9caf-aaaf-4b15b9004a6a\\\"}\"', '{\n  \"page_no\": 16,\n  \"questions\": [\n    {\n      \"question_no\": \"未编号\",\n      \"section_title\": \"\",\n      \"question_type\": \"computation\",\n      \"stem\": \"点B到直线AP的距离d=12√5/5，设B(x₀,y₀)，则{|x₀+2y₀−6|/√5=12√5/5, x₀²/12+y₀²/9=1}，解得{x₀=−3, y₀=−3/2}或{x₀=0, y₀=−3}，即B(0,−3)或(−3,−3/2)，以下同法一。\",\n      \"options\": [],\n      \"answer\": \"B(0,−3)或(−3,−3/2)\",\n      \"analysis\": \"本题通过点到直线距离公式与椭圆方程联立求解点B坐标，属于解析几何中典型的代数方法求交点问题。\",\n      \"solution\": \"由点B在椭圆x²/12 + y²/9 = 1上，且到直线AP（方程为x+2y−6=0）的距离为12√5/5，利用点到直线距离公式列方程，联立椭圆方程，解得两组解：(x₀, y₀) = (−3, −3/2) 或 (0, −3)。\",\n      \"comment\": \"本题考查点到直线距离公式、椭圆标准方程及方程组求解能力，计算需注意绝对值的分情况讨论。\",\n      \"knowledge_points\": [\"点到直线距离公式\", \"椭圆标准方程\", \"方程组求解\", \"绝对值方程\"],\n      \"difficulty\": 4,\n      \"bbox\": [85, 55, 640, 260],\n      \"region_json\": {\"x1\": 0, \"y1\": 0, \"x2\": 1000, \"y2\": 2000},\n      \"confidence\": 0.98,\n      \"images\": [],\n      \"page_end\": 16,\n      \"need_review_reason\": \"\",\n      \"raw_explanation\": \"\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"question_no\": \"未编号\",\n      \"section_title\": \"\",\n      \"question_type\": \"computation\",\n      \"stem\": \"法三：同法一得到直线AP的方程为x+2y−6=0，点B到直线AP的距离d=12√5/5，设B(2√3 cosθ, 3 sinθ)，其中θ∈[0,2π)，则有|2√3 cosθ+6 sinθ−6|/√5=12√5/5，联立cos²θ+sin²θ=1，解得{cosθ=−√3/2, sinθ=−1/2}或{cosθ=0, sinθ=−1}，即B(0,−3)或(−3,−3/2)，以下同法一；\",\n      \"options\": [],\n      \"answer\": \"B(0,−3)或(−3,−3/2)\",\n      \"analysis\": \"本题采用参数方程法（椭圆的三角参数化）求解点B坐标，将几何条件转化为三角恒等式求解。\",\n      \"solution\": \"设B点坐标为椭圆参数形式(2√3 cosθ, 3 sinθ)，代入点到直线距离公式，化简得|2√3 cosθ + 6 sinθ − 6| = 12，结合cos²θ + sin²θ = 1，解得两组三角函数值，对应两点坐标。\",\n      \"comment\": \"参数法是处理椭圆上动点问题的有效手段，可避免二次方程判别式复杂性，但需熟练掌握三角恒等变换。\",\n      \"knowledge_points\": [\"椭圆参数方程\", \"三角恒等式\", \"点到直线距离公式\", \"三角方程求解\"],\n      \"difficulty\": 4,\n      \"bbox\": [85, 285, 725, 600],\n      \"region_json\": {\"x1\": 0, \"y1\": 0, \"x2\": 1000, \"y2\": 2000},\n      \"confidence\": 0.97,\n      \"images\": [],\n      \"page_end\": 16,\n      \"need_review_reason\": \"\",\n      \"raw_explanation\": \"\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"question_no\": \"未编号\",\n      \"section_title\": \"\",\n      \"question_type\": \"computation\",\n      \"stem\": \"法四：当直线AB的斜率不存在时，此时B(0,−3)，S△PAB=1/2×6×3=9，符合题意，此时k_l=3/2，直线l的方程为y=3/2 x−3，即3x−2y−6=0；当直线AB的斜率存在时，设直线AB的方程为y=kx+3，联立椭圆方程有{x²/12+y²/9=1}，则(4k²+3)x²+24kx=0，其中k≠k_AP，即k≠−1/2，\",\n      \"options\": [],\n      \"answer\": \"直线l的方程为3x−2y−6=0 或 (4k²+3)x²+24kx=0（k≠−1/2）\",\n      \"analysis\": \"本题分斜率存在与不存在两种情况讨论，结合三角形面积条件与椭圆联立，推导直线方程。\",\n      \"solution\": \"先考虑AB垂直x轴（斜率不存在），得B(0,−3)，验证面积S△PAB=9成立，进而求出直线l斜率为3/2，得方程3x−2y−6=0；再设AB斜率为k，联立椭圆方程消元后得关于x的二次方程(4k²+3)x²+24kx=0，并排除k=−1/2（与AP平行）的情况。\",\n      \"comment\": \"分类讨论思想在解析几何中至关重要，尤其涉及斜率是否存在、直线是否过定点等问题时必须严谨。\",\n      \"knowledge_points\": [\"直线斜率分类讨论\", \"三角形面积公式\", \"直线与椭圆联立方程\", \"参数限制条件\"],\n      \"difficulty\": 5,\n      \"bbox\": [85, 625, 835, 845],\n      \"region_json\": {\"x1\": 0, \"y1\": 0, \"x2\": 1000, \"y2\": 2000},\n      \"confidence\": 0.96,\n      \"images\": [],\n      \"page_end\": 16,\n      \"need_review_reason\": \"\",\n      \"raw_explanation\": \"\"\n    }\n  ]\n}', 1, NULL, 47798, '2026-05-08 14:56:54.127590', 1, 49, NULL);
INSERT INTO `tiku_ai_parse_result` VALUES (50, 'qwen3-vl-plus', NULL, NULL, '\"{\\\"choices\\\": [{\\\"message\\\": {\\\"content\\\": \\\"{\\\\n  \\\\\\\"page_no\\\\\\\": 17,\\\\n  \\\\\\\"questions\\\\\\\": [\\\\n    {\\\\n      \\\\\\\"question_no\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"未标注\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"section_title\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"question_type\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"computation\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"stem\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"解得x=0或x=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{-24k}{4k^2+3}，k\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\neq0，k\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\neq-\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{1}{2}；令x=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{-24k}{4k^2+3}，则y=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{-12k^2+9}{4k^2+3}，则B\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\left(\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{-24k}{4k^2+3},\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{-12k^2+9}{4k^2+3}\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\right)；同法一得到直线AP的方程为x+2y-6=0；点B到直线AP的距离d=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{12\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{5}}{5}；则\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\left|\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{-24k}{4k^2+3}+2\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\times\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{-12k^2+9}{4k^2+3}-6\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\right|}{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{5}}=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{12\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\sqrt{5}}{5}，解得k=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{3}{2}；此时B\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\left(-3,-\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{3}{2}\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\right)，则得到此时k_l=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{1}{2}，直线l的方程为y=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{1}{2}x，即x-2y=0；综上直线l的方程为3x-2y-6=0或x-2y=0。法五：当l的斜率不存在时，l:x=3,B\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\left(3,-\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{3}{2}\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\right),|PB|=3,A到PB距离d=3，此时S_{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\triangle ABP}=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{1}{2}\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\times3\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\times3=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{9}{2}\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\neq9不满足条件。当l的斜率存在时，设PB:y-\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{3}{2}=k(x-3)，令P(x_1,y_1),B(x_2,y_2)，\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\begin{cases}y=k(x-3)+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{3}{2}\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{x^2}{12}+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{y^2}{9}=1\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\end{cases}，消y可得(4k^2+3)x^2-(24k^2-12k)x+36k^2-36k-27=0，\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\Delta=(24k^2-12k)^2-4(4k^2+3)(36k^2-36k-27)>0，且k\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\neq k_{AP}，即k\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\neq-\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\frac{1}{2}。\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"options\\\\\\\": [],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"answer\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"3x-2y-6=0 或 x-2y=0\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"analysis\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"本题为解析几何综合题，涉及直线与椭圆的位置关系、点到直线距离公式、三角形面积计算及分类讨论思想。通过设定参数k表示直线斜率，联立直线与椭圆方程，利用判别式、距离公式和面积条件求解参数k，最终确定直线l的方程。需注意斜率不存在的特殊情况（垂直于x轴）需单独讨论，并验证是否满足面积条件。\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"solution\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"1. 设直线PB斜率为k（k存在时），写出其方程：y - 3/2 = k(x - 3)；\\\\\\\\n2. 联立椭圆方程x²/12 + y²/9 = 1，消元得关于x的一元二次方程；\\\\\\\\n3. 利用点B坐标表达式代入直线AP：x + 2y - 6 = 0，结合点B到AP距离为12√5/5，列绝对值方程求解k = 3/2；\\\\\\\\n4. 得到对应B点坐标(-3, -3/2)，进而得直线l斜率k_l = 1/2，方程为x - 2y = 0；\\\\\\\\n5. 另考虑斜率不存在情形：l: x = 3，计算△ABP面积为9/2 ≠ 9，舍去；\\\\\\\\n6. 综合得直线l方程为3x - 2y - 6 = 0 或 x - 2y = 0。\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"comment\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"本题综合性强，考查学生对解析几何核心方法的掌握程度，包括参数法、联立方程、距离公式、面积公式及分类讨论能力。关键在于准确建立几何量之间的代数关系，并注意排除无效解。\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"knowledge_points\\\\\\\": [\\\\\\\"直线与椭圆的位置关系\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"点到直线的距离公式\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"三角形面积公式\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"分类讨论思想\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"参数法求解解析几何问题\\\\\\\"],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"difficulty\\\\\\\": 4,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"bbox\\\\\\\": [85, 55, 720, 820],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"region_json\\\\\\\": {\\\\\\\"x1\\\\\\\": 0, \\\\\\\"y1\\\\\\\": 0, \\\\\\\"x2\\\\\\\": 1000, \\\\\\\"y2\\\\\\\": 2000},\\\\n      \\\\\\\"confidence\\\\\\\": 0.98,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"images\\\\\\\": [],\\\\n      \\\\\\\"page_end\\\\\\\": 17,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"need_review_reason\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"raw_explanation\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n    }\\\\n  ]\\\\n}\\\", \\\"reasoning_content\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"role\\\": \\\"assistant\\\"}, \\\"finish_reason\\\": \\\"stop\\\", \\\"index\\\": 0, \\\"logprobs\\\": null}], \\\"object\\\": \\\"chat.completion\\\", \\\"usage\\\": {\\\"prompt_tokens\\\": 3583, \\\"completion_tokens\\\": 1216, \\\"total_tokens\\\": 4799, \\\"completion_tokens_details\\\": {\\\"text_tokens\\\": 1216}, \\\"prompt_tokens_details\\\": {\\\"image_tokens\\\": 2522, \\\"text_tokens\\\": 1061, \\\"cached_tokens\\